OL,3,CMan fleeing e-bike fire dangles from
OL,4,Cthird floor window ledge
OL,6,FA man escaping an e-bike fire in east
OL,7,FLondon dangled precariously from a
OL,8,Fthird floor window before being
OL,9,Frescued by firefighters.
OL,11,FDramatic video caught the moment the
OL,12,Fresident clung to a window ledge
OL,13,Fmoments before smoke poured out of the
OL,14,Fflat in Whitechapel.
OL,16,FTwo men couldn't get out on their own
OL,17,Fbecause the exit was blocked by fire
OL,18,Fand one woman was taken to hospital
OL,19,Fafter breathing in smoke.
