OL,6,FDanny McLaughlin, 64, a neighbour who
OL,7,Fwitnessed one of the rescues and
OL,8,Fcaptured it on his phone, said: "I
OL,9,Fheard shouting that woke me up. I
OL,10,Flooked out of one of my windows and
OL,11,Fsaw one of the men hanging from a
OL,12,Fthird-floor window ledge in the
OL,13,Fneighbouring block.
OL,15,F"His legs were being held, to stop him
OL,16,Ffalling, by a neighbour in the window
OL,17,Fof the flat below the fire.
