OL,6,F"There were lots of other residents
OL,7,Fwatching what was goingon including
OL,8,Fsomewho had left theblock where the
OL,9,Ffire was.The fire brigade arrived
OL,10,Fquickly and a firefighter climbed a
OL,11,Fladder which had been manoeuvred into
OL,12,Fposition and the man was safely
OL,13,Fbrought down.
OL,15,F"A lot of residents are now worried
OL,16,Fabout the prospect of e-bike or e-
OL,17,Fscooter battery fires in these blocks
OL,18,Fand whether we will be trapped or hurt
OL,19,Fif another incident occurs."
