OL,3,CMan fleeing e-bike fire dangles from
OL,4,Cthird floor window ledge
OL,6,FThe fire is being treated as
OL,7,Faccidental and is believed to have
OL,8,Fbeen caused by the failure of a
OL,9,Flithium battery pack for a converted e-
OL,10,Fbike charging in a hallway.
OL,12,FBorough Commander for Tower Hamlets,
OL,13,FRichard Tapp, said: "This is sadly yet
OL,14,Fanother example in our borough of the
OL,15,Fdangers e-bikes and e-scooters can
OL,16,Fpose if the battery fails
OL,17,Fcatastrophically and catches fire.
