OL,3,CMan fleeing e-bike fire dangles from
OL,4,Cthird floor window ledge
OL,6,F"This can be caused by reasons
OL,7,Fincluding counterfeit or unsafe
OL,8,Fproducts being sold online, the wrong
OL,9,Fcharger being used, or if components
OL,10,Fare fitted or used incorrectly.
OL,12,F"My crews were on scene in four
OL,13,Fminutes and quickly and professionally
OL,14,Fset about rescuing two people as well
OL,15,Fas tackling the fire.
OL,17,F"A number of e-bikes were being stored
OL,18,Fin the hallway and this fire shows
OL,19,Fjust how dangerous blocking your
OL,20,Fescape route can be.
