OL,3,CMan fleeing e-bike fire dangles from
OL,4,Cthird floor window ledge
OL,6,F"You should keep an e-bike or e-
OL,7,Fscooter outside or in a shed. If this
OL,8,Fis not possible, put it in a room
OL,9,Fwhere you can shut a door and contain
OL,10,Fa fire.
OL,12,F"Although the smoke alarm sounded,
OL,13,Fthis incident also highlights the
OL,14,Frisks of charging whilst people are
OL,15,Fsleeping as there is less time to
OL,16,Freact before the fire intensifies."
